(4, 8, 27, '<p>Modules 1-4 each require a post-module assignment to reinforce what is \r\nlearned in class. In Module 5, the assignment is accomplished during \r\nclass (with some evening work during the module). Each assignment and \r\nassociated readings may require up to 20 hours to complete. Module 6 \r\n(the practicum) involves the design, development, and facilitation of an\r\n actual training program and time requirements vary. Learners usually \r\ncomplete the practicum in 6 months or more of part-time work/study.<br></p>', '<p>Modules 1-4 each require a post-module assignment to reinforce what is \r\nlearned in class. In Module 5, the assignment is accomplished during \r\nclass (with some evening work during the module). Each assignment and \r\nassociated readings may require up to 20 hours to complete. Module 6 \r\n(the practicum) involves the design, development, and facilitation of an\r\n actual training program and time requirements vary. Learners usually \r\ncomplete the practicum in 6 months or more of part-time work/study.<br></p>', '<p>Modules 1-4 each require a post-module assignment to reinforce what is \r\nlearned in class. In Module 5, the assignment is accomplished during \r\nclass (with some evening work during the module). Each assignment and \r\nassociated readings may require up to 20 hours to complete. Module 6 \r\n(the practicum) involves the design, development, and facilitation of an\r\n actual training program and time requirements vary. Learners usually \r\ncomplete the practicum in 6 months or more of part-time work/study.<br></p>', NULL, 'I', '47.15.11.173', '2017-08-31 20:17:45', '2017-08-31 20:17:45'),
(5, 8, 1, '<p>I was in similar situation (although in different field - technical texts editing) - getting to be self-employed freelancer. I also was not sure how to communicate when in "selling myself" situation. As I am in the Czech republic, I took the following web-based courses - <a href="https://www.evyna.cz/kurzy">https://www.evyna.cz/kurzy</a> - which, if you can read in the Czech language, you will see are designed to support people in transition into the self-employed or starting entrepreneur position. The courses were for free for registered participants.<br></p>', '<p>The web-based courses on self-awareness and communication provided me with a good basis and understanding of what is important in presenting myself as a "self-selling" professional. The courses were well designed and smooth to take.<br></p>', '<p>As I wrote above, the learning outcome was my better confidence, self-awareness and understanding of the important things when communicating as a professional freelancer. Given it was web-based, it did not teach me one thing - the in-person practicing of the communication style and techniques. However, it set me well to... go and practice in real life!<br></p>', NULL, 'A', '47.15.11.173', '2017-08-31 20:21:22', '2018-02-05 16:14:16'),
